            </svg>
            moroccancitrus.de
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-anthracite-800 rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-anthracite-700 hover:border-gold-500/30 transition-colors">
        <div class="p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
            <span class="text-sm text-gold-500 font-medium">2014 - 2021</span>
            <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-anthracite-600 text-gray-400 rounded-full text-xs">Abgeschlossen</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">ERP-System Pharmabranche</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4">Architektur, Konzeption und Entwicklung eines ERP-Systems für Vertrieb und Produktion. Projektleitung von Design bis Integration.</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-anthracite-700 text-gray-400 rounded text-xs">WPF</span>
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-anthracite-700 text-gray-400 rounded text-xs">C#</span>
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-anthracite-700 text-gray-400 rounded text-xs">Oracle</span>
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-anthracite-700 text-gray-400 rounded text-xs">WCF Services</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-anthracite-800 rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-anthracite-700 hover:border-gold-500/30 transition-colors">
        <div class="p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
            <span class="text-sm text-gold-500 font-medium">2020 - 2022</span>
            <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-anthracite-600 text-gray-400 rounded-full text-xs">Abgeschlossen</span>
          </div>
