          <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4">Weiterentwicklung eines HR-Systems für Vertrieb und Mitarbeiterbeschaffung in der Recruiting-Branche.</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-anthracite-700 text-gray-400 rounded text-xs">WPF</span>
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-anthracite-700 text-gray-400 rounded text-xs">.NET Core</span>
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-anthracite-700 text-gray-400 rounded text-xs">MVVM</span>
