            <span class="text-sm text-gold-500 font-medium">2007 - 2011</span>
            <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-anthracite-600 text-gray-400 rounded-full text-xs">Abgeschlossen</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Kundeninformationssystem Pharma</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4">Konzeption und Weiterentwicklung mit Einkauf, Logistik, Produktionsverwaltung und Lagerverwaltung.</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-anthracite-700 text-gray-400 rounded text-xs">C#</span>
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-anthracite-700 text-gray-400 rounded text-xs">ASP.NET</span>
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-anthracite-700 text-gray-400 rounded text-xs">Oracle</span>
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-anthracite-700 text-gray-400 rounded text-xs">Crystal Reports</span>
